      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 367469116919808
    m_Localized: Your field of view increases by {values[0]}m, but you also become
      visible to enemies.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 367469746065408
    m_Localized: The number of bullets in the gun increases by {values[0]} times,
      but the reload time increases by {values[1]} times.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 367470446514176
    m_Localized: HP becomes {values[0]} times, but movement speed becomes {values[1]}
      times.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 367471146962944
    m_Localized: 'Gun damage is multiplied by {values[0]}, but

      RPS and bullet
      velocity are multiplied by {values[1]}.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 367472891793408
    m_Localized: 'Gun damage is multiplied by {values[0]}, but

      RPS and bullet
      velocity are multiplied by {values[1]}.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 367762474930176
    m_Localized: 'The distance of sound increases by {values[0]}, but

      The
      distance at which sound can be heard increases by {values[1]}%.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 367763871633408
    m_Localized: 'Kill score is multiplied by {values[0]}

      Headkill score
      is multiplied by {values[1]}'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 367995229442048
    m_Localized: 'While waiting to respawn after death,

      gadgets and special
      moves become available,

      and you can move at {values[1]}% speed,

      but
      the time until respawn increases by {values[0]}%.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368094353428480
    m_Localized: 'The amount of damage received increases by {values[0]}%, but

      when
      HP reaches zero,

      damage is prevented by using the damage as a substitute
      for HP.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368095318118400
    m_Localized: 'When critically injured:

      Movement speed increases by {values[0]}%,
      but

      Enemy kill score increases by {values[1]}%.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368096014372864
    m_Localized: 'The player''s size decreases by {values[0]}%, but

      HP decreases
      by {values[1]}%.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368176956051456
    m_Localized: 'The player''s size increases by {values[0]}%, but

      HP increases
      by {values[1]}%.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368305075261440
    m_Localized: "The location of the last opponent you killed will now be displayed
      on the minimap,\r\n and your score will increase by an additional {values[0]}
      when you kill someone,\r\n but if you are killed by the same opponent, your
      score will decrease by {values[1]}."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368305914122240
    m_Localized: 'While a dodge check is active,

      the score increases by {values[0]}
      per second, but

      HP decreases by {values[1]}%.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368306471964672
    m_Localized: You can breathe in the water, but you will suffocate anywhere else.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368485266755584
    m_Localized: 'Movement speed decreases by {values[0]}%, but

      Movement
      speed increases by {values[1]}% in slow areas.

      (Slowing effect is not
      negated)'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368597233700864
    m_Localized: 'Disables most areas, but

      Knockback resistance is reduced
      by {values[0]}%

      Sound distance during movement is increased by {values[1]}%'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368640367923200
    m_Localized: 'The surrounding area becomes obscured,

      and the forward
      field of view angle becomes {values[0]}%,

      but the cost increases.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368686073253888
    m_Localized: 'HP decreases by {values[0]}%, but

      cost increases'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368738845986816
    m_Localized: 'Reload time increases by {values[0]}%, but

      cost increases.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368815664664576
    m_Localized: If you are within {values[0]}m on the minimap, your position will
      be revealed to the enemy, but the cost will increase.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368816365113344
    m_Localized: The range over which sound can be heard decreases by {values[0]}%,
      but the cost increases.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 368882626727936
    m_Localized: 'Upon death,

      Gadget Stock decreases by {stringlvs[0]}%

      Special
      Gauge decreases by {values[0]}%

      but cost increases.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 369097207320576
    m_Localized: 'The enemy''s HP UI will no longer be displayed, but

      the
      cost will increase.

      <s>This has always been the case until now</s>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 369202324967424
    m_Localized: "Speed \u200B\u200Breduction in the area increases by {values[0]}%\r\nDamage
      taken from the area increases by {values[1]}% but\r\nCost increases"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
